    DiffEqUncertainty.jl

    DiffEqUncertainty.jl is a component package in the DifferentialEquations ecosystem. It holds the utilities for solving uncertainty quantification. Users interested in using this functionality should check out DifferentialEquations.jl.

    Note: This is a work in progress!
